                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#200r"/>
                                    <desc type="PoemQene"> It is <term key="Sellase" ana="#Sellase"> ሥላሴ፡</term> <term key="Qene" ana="#Qene">Qǝne</term> performed for King <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7481NaodA">Nāʿod</persName>, 
                                        when he was at <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2246DabraB">Dabra Bǝrhān</placeName>.
                                        </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሥላሴ፡ ዘንጉሥነ፡ ናኦድ፡ ወበጸጋ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘተሰምየ፡ አንበሳ፡
                                        በፀር፡ ዘተቀንየ፡  እንዘ፡ ሀሎ፡ በደብረ፡ ብርሃን፡  አመ፡  ፩፡ ለመጋቢት፡  በበዓለ፡   ልደታ፡ ለእግዚእትነ፡ ማርያም። </q>
                                
                                
